item.title: Hello World
item.description: What? I feel like starting a simple blog where I can write about projects I am working on, problems I run in to, and eventually the solutions to those problems. I will also be writing about any tips, tricks and cool tools I run in to throughout the process. Why? To be honest, I do not expect anyone to be reading this at all. I just want some place to write about technology that excite and sometimes annoy me.
